    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"110064\">Kenny Lau</span> <a href=\"#narrow/channel/113489-new-members/topic/Splitting.20to.20x.3D0.20and.20x.3E0.20cases.20when.20x.3E.3D0.20is.20known/near/555592791\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"952635\">Michael Novak</span> btw you should use b le a over a ge b</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>You're right, thanks for the reminder!</p>",
